quran[1]{c,v,t}:
  2,282,"Ko onon yo gom…óim…ďe Alla e Nulaa…óo, si on √Īawlondirii hakkunde mo'on haa e lajal happaangal, winndee nden √Īamaande: yo winndiroowo winndir nun…óal e shari'a, wata on salo winndirde ngal nunn…óal wano Alla Annidiri mo non ka Deftere Makko. Yo Winndu kon ko jom √Īamaande nden woni e hoore mu'un; fii no on [√Īawlaa…óo] qirritora. Yo o hulu Alla, hara o ustaali huunde e √Īamaande nden. Si on mo √Īamaande woni e mun laatike …óay…óo maa feetu…óo mo waawanaa hoore mu'un, maa hara o waawataa fitude sabu mboboyaagal maa ko nanndi; yo waliyuu makko on fitiraŇč mo nun…óal. ∆äa…ď…ďee seedee…ďe …ói…óo wor…ďe hellifaa…ďe nun…óu…ďe: si …ďe laataaki wor…ďe …ói…óo, seedinee gorko gooto e rew…ďe …ói…óo immorde e …ďen …ďe wela-…óon diina e nun…óal mu'un; fii si gooto e rew…ďe …ďen yejjitii, oya anndiŇčtina mo. Wata seedee…ďe …ďen salo seedagol e √Īamaande nden si …ďe noddaama fii mun, wata aamere ha…óu on winndugol √Īamaande nden -…óuu…ói fam…ói- haa e lajal mayre; ko winndugol √Īamaande nden …ďuri nun…óude ka shari'a, ko …óum kadi …ďurata nii…ďnude seedeeyaagal ngal, …ďura …ďa…ótinnde e ittitugol sikke √Īamaande nden (noone mayre e emmbere mayre). Si wanaa hara tokkugol ahadi ndin hakkunde mo'on ko e ngeyngu ngu yiilindirton; bakkaatu fawaaki on si on winndaali kon ko hatonjinaa e winndugol, ko woorugol poo…óondiral winndugol ngol shar'iniraa. Dagotaako lorrude winndoowo on e seedotoo…ďe …ďen, kam…ďe kadi …ďe haanaa lorrirde kon ko …ďe …óa…ď…ďiraa winndugol maa seedagol, si on lorrindirii fii …óum, haray on yaltii e …óoftaare Alla. Hulee Alla -onon muumini en- huuron Yamirooje Makko, wo…ó…óito-…óon Ha…óaa…ói Makko. Alla No Anndina on mo∆ī∆īere mon aduna e laakara, Alla Ko Anndu…óo kala huunde."